# Cursor AI Agent Configuration

This project uses AgentKit for AI agent management.

## Agent Files Location

Agent files are organized in: `Agent/`

## Usage with Cursor

### Method 1: @-mentions (Recommended)

Use @-mentions to reference specific agents:

```
@Agent/engineering/backend-architect.md Design a REST API
```

### Method 2: Natural Language

Reference agents naturally in your prompts:

```
"Following the backend-architect guidelines in Agent/engineering/..."
```

